	<p>If you plan to exhibit your dog and first came to the exhibition with it, then you might be interested to know what the abbreviation of exhibition titles means. <br> This is not just a set of letters, but quite specific international names of certain titles assigned at dog shows all over the world. <br> Let's see what lies behind all these CACs, BISs, CACIBs.</p>
